text: Walter Müller (born 31 December 1930) is a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics, representing Saar. ==See also== * Saar at the 1952 Summer Olympics ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Saar Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Neunkirchen, Saarland
title: Walter Müller (German gymnast)
